title: Ep - 115 - MATT ROLOFF FROM LITTLE PEOPLE BIG WORLD
description:
Matt Roloff is best known for participating with his family on the TLC reality television program, Little People, Big World. Roloff has dwarfism, as does his ex-wife Amy and one of their four children, Zachary.


Michele Laikowski, producer on The Jenny McCarthy Show, discusses with Kate the new show Dr. Pimple Popper on TLC. Every week dermatologist Sandra Lee, MD, meets with men and women suffering from rare, often confidence-crushing skin conditions. 


Jimmy Bailey is a Navy commander, orthopedic surgeon, and father of five children. He has never watched any episode of Real Housewives, so naturally Kate asked him to review the season premiere of Real Housewives of Orange County.
